{{flavour|A potion which hides you from the sight of others.}}

[[Quaff]]ing a '''potion of invisibility''' makes your character [[invisibility|invisible]] for <code>1d40 + 14</code> turns (15-54 turns, 35 turns on average). If you were already invisible, your invisibility will be extended by <code>1d40 - 1</code> turns, up to 100.

 "You fade into invisibility!"
 "You feel safely hidden away." (if already invisible)

See the [[Invisible]] page for details on the [[status effect]] and its uses.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.28]], sources of invisibility would inflict [[magic contamination]] over time.

